'''碘酸钙'''（化学式：[[钙|Ca]]([[碘酸根|IO<sub>3</sub>]])<sub>2</sub>）是一种无机化合物。在[[智利|智利]]的[[阿他加马沙漠|阿他加马沙漠]]发现。<ref>{{Cite book | author = Lyday，Phyllis A. | title = "Iodine and Iodine Compounds" in Ullmann's Encyclopedia of Industrial Chemistry | location =  | publisher =  | date =  | pages = 382-390 | ISBN = 978-3-527-30673-2 | accessdate =  | url = http://onlinelibrary.wiley.com/doi/10.1002/14356007.a14_381/abstract;jsessionid=C58B454E274ED44C30BA00959303E339.f02t02 | language = en | quote =  | archive-date = 2016-03-07 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160307160327/http://onlinelibrary.wiley.com/doi/10.1002/14356007.a14_381/abstract;jsessionid=C58B454E274ED44C30BA00959303E339.f02t02 | dead-url = no }}</ref>

==制取==

[[碘|碘]]在[[酸性|酸性]]条件下被氯酸钾氧化成[[碘酸氢钾|碘酸氢钾]]：

:{{反應式|2|K|Cl|O|3|+|H|Cl|+|I|2|eq|K|I|O|3}}·{{反應式|H|I|O|3|+|Cl|2|↑|+|K|Cl}}

经[[氢氧化钾|氢氧化钾]]中和后，与[[氯化钙|氯化钙]]反应生成碘酸钙。

:{{反應式|K|I|O|3}}·{{反應式|H|I|O|3|+|K|O|H|eq|2|K|I|O|3|+|H|2|O}}
:{{反應式|2|K|I|O|3|+|Ca|Cl|2|eq|Ca}}({{化學式|I|O|3}})<sub>2</sub>↓+{{反應式|2|K|Cl}}

产生的氯气用氢氧化钾溶液中和后再利用<ref>{{Cite web |url = http://www.docin.com/p-184941621.html |title = 碘酸钙的制备及含量测定 - 豆丁网 |author =  |date =  |publisher =  |language = zh-hans |accessdate =  |quote =  |archive-date = 2015-02-12 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20150212132527/http://www.docin.com/p-184941621.html |dead-url = no }}</ref>：

:{{反應式|Cl|2|+|2|K|O|H|eq|K|Cl|+|K|Cl|O|3|+|H|2|O}}

==用途==
可以用作[[软膏剂|软膏剂]]、[[杀菌剂|杀菌剂]]、[[除臭剂|除臭剂]]。也可以作为[[饲料|饲料]]<ref>{{Cite web |url = http://www.famic.go.jp/ffis/feed/sub3_feedadditives.html |title = 飼料添加物一覧 - 独立行政法人農林水産消費安全技術センター（FAMIC） |author =  |date =  |publisher =  |language = ja |accessdate =  |quote =  |archive-date = 2015-02-12 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20150212141432/http://www.famic.go.jp/ffis/feed/sub3_feedadditives.html |dead-url = no }}</ref>。
